-process-is-not-defined\">报错6：request.js:18 Uncaught ReferenceError: process is not defined</a></li><li class=\"toc-li\"><a class=\"level-1\" href=\"#%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%99\">其他报错</a></li><li class=\"toc-li\"><a class=\"level-1\" href=\"#%E5%8F%82%E8%80%83%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0\">参考文章</a></li></dir><h1 data-lines=\"2\" data-sign=\"dd5a69f82f3ae2ccf02bb8ba0e67f2bc\" id=\"%E6%8F%8F%E8%BF%B0\"><a href=\"#%E6%8F%8F%E8%BF%B0\" class=\"anchor\"></a>描述</h1><p data-lines=\"2\" data-type=\"p\" data-sign=\"e62060056362cc5e039be50e9839d6342\">全过程视频：<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1R64y1J7gW\" title=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1R64y1J7gW\">www.bilibili.com/vid...</a></p><p data-lines=\"2\" data-type=\"p\" data-sign=\"d5424864c5b7d78dea1de87badc315792\">feat_1.2.x_studio-ui_vue2_vite：基于ruoyi-vue的vue2改用为vite全方位指南【2024.9.8】</p><hr data-lines=\"2\" data-sign=\"hr2\"><h1 data-lines=\"2\" data-sign=\"b61794d68ea2645a643cbd92af6f81f2\" id=\"%E5%89%8D%E6%9C%9F%E6%AD%A5%E9%AA%A4\"><a href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E6%9C%9F%E6%AD%A5%E9%AA%A4\" class=\"anchor\"></a>前期步骤</h1><p data-lines=\"2\" data-type=\"p\" data-sign=\"172c88ac48decf977488b0ab5fa975442\">重新构建项目，按照原始的四个步骤，创建一个vue2+vite的工程项目。</p><p data-lines=\"3\" data-type=\"br\" data-sign=\"br3\">&nbsp;</p><hr data-lines=\"1\" data-sign=\"hr1\"><h1 data-lines=\"2\" data-sign=\"f98868e1d21783f02b8cc88f7b5cf8db\" id=\"%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%991%EF%BC%9Afailed-to-resolve-import-%E2%80%9Ccomponentslayoutsidebar%E2%80%9C\"><a href=\"#%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%991%EF%BC%9Afailed-to-resolve-import-%E2%80%9Ccomponentslayoutsidebar%E2%80%9C\" class=\"anchor\"></a>报错1：Failed to resolve import “@/components/Layout/SideBar“</h1><p data-lines=\"2\" data-type=\"p\" data-sign=\"b2e63eac56d61d6e892f8be0c27f24972\"><img alt=\"image-20240907213753918\" src=\"https://pictured-bed.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/2024/202409072137209.png\">  </p><p data-lines=\"2\" data-type=\"p\" data-sign=\"418b932eab11d1d142c13da6ed85dbaf2\"><strong>解决方案：</strong></p><p data-lines=\"2\" data-type=\"p\" data-sign=\"521198c248d38e00d8ab20f3722b9fda2\">在vite.config.js文件中添加扩展，保存后重新运行即可</p><div data-sign=\"1d60204071e215e715e29d254e5705b1\" data-type=\"codeBlock\" data-lines=\"4\">\n      <select id=\"code-preview-lang-select\" style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cherry-code-preview-lang-select\">\n      <option value=\"\" selected=\"\" disabled=\"\" hidden=\"\">Choose here</option>\n      <option value=\"javascript\">javascript</option><option value=\"typescript\">typescript</option><option value=\"html\">html</option><option value=\"css\">css</option><option value=\"shell\">shell</option><option value=\"python\">python</option><option value=\"golang\">golang</option><option value=\"java\">java</option><option value=\"c\">c</option><option value=\"c++\">c++</option><option value=\"c#\">c#</option><option value=\"php\">php</option><option value=\"ruby\">ruby</option><option value=\"swift\">swift</option><option value=\"kotlin\">kotlin</option><option value=\"scala\">scala</option><option value=\"rust\">rust</option><option value=\"dart\">dart</option><option value=\"elixir\">elixir</option><option value=\"haskell\">haskell</option><option value=\"lua\">lua</option><option value=\"perl\">perl</option><option value=\"r\">r</option><option value=\"sql\">sql</option>\n    </select>\n      <div class=\"cherry-copy-code-block\" style=\"display:none;\"><i class=\"ch-icon ch-icon-copy\" title=\"copy\"></i></div>\n      <pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js wrap\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"token literal-property property\">extensions</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\'.js\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\'.jsx\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\'.ts\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\'.tsx\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\'.json\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\'.vue\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></span></code></pre>\n    </div><p data-lines=\"2\" data-type=\"p\" data-sign=\"dcbc99ad45a0956be28564f36ae53f8e2\"><img alt=\"image-20240907213949367\" src=\"https://pictured-bed.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/2024/202409072139469.png\">  </p><p data-lines=\"3\" data-type=\"br\" data-sign=\"br3\">&nbsp;</p><h1 data-lines=\"1\" data-sign=\"dc1d1cf3239112112baeafcddb8fa53c\" id=\"%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%992%EF%BC%9A-error-the-jsx-syntax-extension-is-not-currently-enabled\"><a href=\"#%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%992%EF%BC%9A-error-the-jsx-syntax-extension-is-not-currently-enabled\" class=\"anchor\"></a>报错2： [ERROR] The JSX syntax extension is not currently enabled</h1><ol class=\"cherry-list__default\" start=\"1\" data-sign=\"aa458126dcc612f93434dfd4f6ca50ad\" data-lines=\"2\"><li><p><strong>安装 JSX 支持依赖</strong></p></li></ol><p data-lines=\"2\" data-type=\"p\" data-sign=\"ef62f0c265d104afc09576ea04fe0e6c2\">首先，你需要安装 <code>@vue/babel-preset-jsx</code> 来支持 JSX 语法。</p><div data-sign=\"2f0c583100a8ebb9307b46849217bccf\" data-type=\"codeBlock\" data-lines=\"4\">\n      <select id=\"code-preview-lang-select\" style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cherry-code-preview-lang-select\">\n      <option value=\"\" selected=\"\" disabled=\"\" hidden=\"\">Choose here</option>\n      <option value=\"javascript\">javascript</option><option value=\"typescript\">typescript</option><option value=\"html\">html</option><option value=\"css\">css</option><option value=\"shell\">shell</option><option value=\"python\">python</option><option value=\"golang\">golang</option><option value=\"java\">java</option><option value=\"c\">c</option><option value=\"c++\">c++</option><option value=\"c#\">c#</option><option value=\"php\">php</option><option value=\"ruby\">ruby</option><option value=\"swift\">swift</option><option value=\"kotlin\">kotlin</option><option value=\"scala\">scala</option><option value=\"rust\">rust</option><option value=\"dart\">dart</option><option value=\"elixir\">elixir</option><option value=\"haskell\">haskell</option><option value=\"lua\">lua</option><option value=\"perl\">perl</option><option value=\"r\">r</option><option value=\"sql\">sql</option>\n    </select>\n      <div class=\"cherry-copy-code-block\" style=\"display:none;\"><i class=\"ch-icon ch-icon-copy\" title=\"copy\"></i></div>\n      <pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash wrap\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> @vue/babel-preset-jsx --save-dev</span></code></pre>\n    </div><ol class=\"cherry-list__default\" start=\"2\" data-sign=\"ebc05d87d9a55264bd723f022fae2529\" data-lines=\"2\"><li><p><strong>配置 Babel</strong></p></li></ol><p data-lines=\"2\" data-type=\"p\" data-sign=\"ab8b3395f3e5035f9f612e9a43a12fc82\">在项目根目录下，创建或更新 <code>babel.config.js</code> 文件，添加 JSX 支持的配置：</p><div data-sign=\"d0972fa3c29b0e13f62aeace5564352c\" data-type=\"codeBlock\" data-lines=\"8\">\n      <select id=\"code-preview-lang-select\" style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cherry-code-preview-lang-select\">\n      <option value=\"\" selected=\"\" disabled=\"\" hidden=\"\">Choose here</option>\n      <option value=\"javascript\" selected=\"selected\">javascript</option><option value=\"typescript\">typescript</option><option value=\"html\">html</option><option value=\"css\">css</option><option value=\"shell\">shell</option><option value=\"python\">python</option><option value=\"golang\">golang</option><option value=\"java\">java</option><option value=\"c\">c</option><option value=\"c++\">c++</option><option value=\"c#\">c#</option><option value=\"php\">php</option><option value=\"ruby\">ruby</option><option value=\"swift\">swift</option><option value=\"kotlin\">kotlin</option><option value=\"scala\">scala</option><option value=\"rust\">rust</option><option value=\"dart\">dart</option><option value=\"elixir\">elixir</option><option value=\"haskell\">haskell</option><option value=\"lua\">lua</option><option value=\"perl\">perl</option><option value=\"r\">r</option><option value=\"sql\">sql</option>\n    </select>\n      <div class=\"cherry-copy-code-block\" style=\"display:none;\"><i class=\"ch-icon ch-icon-copy\" title=\"copy\"></i></div>\n      <pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript wrap\"><span class=\"code-line\">module<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-line\">  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">presets</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-line\">    <span class=\"token string\">\'@vue/babel-preset-jsx\'</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-line\">  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span></code></pre>\n    </div><ol class=\"cherry-list__default\" start=\"3\" data-sign=\"8f6c32f4b99ed67360f09be5abee6e94\" data-lines=\"2\"><li><p><strong>配置 Vite</strong></p></li></ol><p data-lines=\"2\" data-type=\"p\" data-sign=\"64129bf60fabfaef70985d2bdaa6408e2\">由于你正在使用 Vue 2，你需要确保 Vite 插件正确地处理 <code>.vue</code> 文件中的 JSX。这通常涉及到配置 Vite 插件。在你的 <code>vite.config.js</code> 文件中，你需要添加或更新插件配置：</p><div data-sign=\"d29ad446cb98424bcdcbdf8ecc17b9b6\" data-type=\"codeBlock\" data-lines=\"9\">\n      <select id=\"code-preview-lang-select\" style=\"display:none;\" class=\"cherry-code-preview-lang-select\">\n      <option value=\"\" selected=\"\" disabled=\"\" hidden=\"\">Choose here</option>\n      <option value=\"javascript\" selected=\"selected\">javascript</option><option value=\"typescript\">typescript</option><option value=\"html\">html</option><option value=\"css\">css</option><option value=\"shell\">shell</option><option value=\"python\">python</option><option value=\"golang\">golang</option><option value=\"java\">java</option><option value=\"c\">c</option><option value=\"c++\">c++</option><option value=\"c#\">c#</option><option value=\"php\">php</option><option value=\"ruby\">ruby</option><option value=\"swift\">swift</option><option value=\"kotlin\">kotlin</option><option value=\"scala\">scala</option><option value=\"rust\">rust</option><option value=\"dart\">dart</option><option value=\"elixir\">elixir</option><option value=\"haskell\">haskell</option><option value=\"lua\">lua</option><option value=\"perl\">perl</option><option value=\"r\">r</option><option value=\"sql\">sql</option>\n    </select>\n      <div class=\"cherry-copy-code-block\" style=\"display:none;\"><i class=\"ch-icon ch-icon-copy\" title=\"copy\"></i></div>\n      <pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript wrap\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> defineConfig <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\'vite\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> vue <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\'@vitejs/plugin-vue2\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-line\"></span>\n<span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"token function\">defineConfig</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"code-line\">  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">plugins</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=